# --- goalify's own state / generated goal files ---
# goalify writes /goal execution files under .goal/ in a project. They are
# single-use and self-deleting; never commit them (they hold absolute paths and
# project-specific context). Keep this repo generic.
.goal/
*-goal.md
goal-*.md

